11827 /// Model horizontal reductions.
11828 ///
11829 /// A horizontal reduction is a tree of reduction instructions that has values
11830 /// that can be put into a vector as its leaves. For example:
11831 ///
11832 /// mul mul mul mul
11833 ///  \  /    \  /
11834 ///   +       +
11835 ///    \     /
11836 ///       +
