11838 /// instructions. A reduction can feed into a store or a binary operation
11839 /// feeding a phi.
11840 ///    ...
11841 ///    \  /
11842 ///     +
11843 ///     |
11844 ///  phi +=
11845 ///
11846 ///  Or:
11847 ///    ...
11848 ///    \  /
11849 ///     +
11850 ///     |
11851 ///   *p =
11852 ///
